 Queue:
       Queue follows FIFO (First In First Out)
            Insert → Rear (end)
            Remove → Front (start)
      Head & Tail Pointers:
            head → removal
            tail → insertion
      Resizing:
            When full → resize (double size)
            Copy elements in order
 Queue Hierarchy:
            Collection
               ↓
            Queue (Interface)
               ↓
            Deque (sub-interface)

Core Queue Methods:
      Method	Purpose	      Behavior
      offer(e)	Add element	      returns false if fails
      add(e)	Add element	      throws exception if fails
      poll()	Remove head	      returns null if empty
      remove()	Remove head	      throws exception
      peek()	View head	      returns null
      element()	View head	      throws exception

      offer() vs add() → safe vs exception
      poll() vs remove() → safe vs exception
      peek() vs element() → safe vs exception

